
Using gradle:
First, install gradle, at least version 2.6

Example gradle commands you can use
gradle build
gradle check
gradle uploadArchives //e.g. to "publish" the jar


Credits:

Following examples:
http://www.mkyong.com/gradle/gradle-create-a-jar-file-with-dependencies/
https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/tutorial_java_projects.html

